      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FOURTHTIMELUCKY (8) has progressed nicely in his last couple of runs. Finished third at Wodonga two starts back then got the job done by a nose as public elect last time out. No reason he can't keep the ball rolling. BEFORE THE WAR (2) turned in a nice effort to score two runs ago at Wodonga. Thrown in the deep end last time when sent to time but still held his own to some degree. Finds a suitable assignment and is one of the key chances. GETTY (5) returns and will give them something to catch from the inside pillar. If they leave him alone he might just steal it. MATHRIN (3) has been struggling of late but has peaks that measure up. Keeping safe.",
